t runs on, so that developers can write C/C++ applications that run on any Mbed-enabled board.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T18:42:42.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"HQarroum/awesome-iot","categoryHTML":"<h4>Programming languages</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.rust-lang.org/\">Rust</a> - Rust is a language focused on performance, reliability and productivity. It is known for its safety, it is memory safe, it uses a borrow checker, and concurrency is also safe.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T18:42:42.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"HQarroum/awesome-iot","categoryHTML":"<h4>Middlewares</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://thingspeak.com/\">Thingspeak</a> -  An open-source IoT analytics platform service that allows you to aggregate, visualize, and analyze live data streams in the cloud. You can send data to ThingSpeak from your devices, create instant visualization of live data, and send alerts.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T18:42:42.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"vuejs/awesome-vue","categoryHTML":"<h2>Components &#x26; Libraries</h2><h3>Scaffold</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/huogerac/crud-vuetify-structured-template\">vuejs-vuetify-structured-template boilerplate</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/huogerac/crud-vuetify-structured-template\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">21</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":21,\"repo\":\"huogerac/crud-vuetify-structured-template\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - A vue-cli template for a full-featured Vuejs + Vuetify + Great structure + API Ready</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T16:58:43.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"APA-Technology-Division/urban-and-regional-planning-resources","categoryHTML":"<h2>Public Data Resources</h2><h3>Employment</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://lehd.ces.census.gov/\">Longitudinal Employer-Household Dynamics (LEHD)</a> -  The LEHD program combines these administrative data, and data from censuses and surveys. From these data, the program creates statistics on employment, earnings, and job flows at detailed levels of geography and industry and for different demographic groups. Additional Information: <a href=\"https://onthemap.ces.census.gov/\">On The Map Download Page</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T16:56:06.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"APA-Technology-Division/urban-and-regional-planning-resources","categoryHTML":"<h2>Public Data Resources</h2><h3>Equity and Environmental Justice</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.epa.gov/ejscreen/understanding-ejscreen-results\">EJ Screen</a> - EJSCREEN uses maps and reports to present three kinds of information: Environmental indicators, demographic indicators and EJ Indexes. Additional Information: <a href=\"https://www.epa.gov/ejscreen/download-ejscreen-data\">Download</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T16:56:06.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"APA-Technology-Division/urban-and-regional-planning-resources","categoryHTML":"<h2>Public Data Resources</h2><h3>Transportation</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://transit.land\">Transitland</a> - Transitland is an open data platform that collects GTFS, GTFS Realtime, and other open data feeds from over 2,500 transit operators in over 55 countries. Additional Information: <a href=\"https://www.interline.io/\">Interline</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/transitland\">GitHub</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T16:56:06.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"APA-Technology-Division/urban-and-regional-planning-resources","categoryHTML":"<h2>Public Data Resources</h2><h3>Transportation</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://geoffboeing.com/publications/street-network-models-indicators-world/\">Global Urban Street Networks</a> - Ready‐to‐use global street network models and calculated indicators in a GIS format. Additional Information: <a href=\"https://dataverse.harvard.edu/dataset.xhtml?persistentId=doi:10.7910/DVN/E5TPDQ\">Geopackage Download</a></li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T16:56:06.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"APA-Technology-Division/urban-and-regional-planning-resources","categoryHTML":"<h2>Planning Data Specifications</h2><h3>Transportation</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.curblr.org\">CurbLR</a> -  An open data specification for curb regulations maintained by SharedStreets. Additional Information: <a href=\"https://www.github.com/sharedstreets/curblr\">GitHub</a>, Demo: Interactive <a href=\"https://demo.curblr.org/\">map and example feed</a>, Blog post: <a href=\"https://medium.com/sharedstreets/crossroads-for-the-curb-be3137154148\">Why CurbLR was built</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T16:56:06.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"APA-Technology-Division/urban-and-regional-planning-resources","categoryHTML":"<h2>Platforms and Software Resources</h2><h3>Geospatial Data and Visualization</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.esri.com/en-us/arcgis/about-arcgis/overview\">ArcGIS</a> - This platform is a geographic information system (GIS) for working with maps and geographic information maintained by the Environmental Systems Research Institute (ESRI).</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T16:56:06.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"gruhn/awesome-naming","categoryHTML":"<h2>Design Patterns and Anti Patterns</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shotgun_surgery\">Shotgun surgery</a> - A programming antipattern where in a single change you wildly add code everywhere in your codebase.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T15:01:06.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-engineering-team-management","categoryHT