targazerCount\":5662,\"repo\":\"crowdsecurity/crowdsec\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - CrowdSec is a free, modern &#x26; collaborative behavior detection engine, coupled with a global IP reputation network. It stacks on Fail2Ban's philosophy but is IPV6 compatible and 60x faster (Go vs Python), uses Grok patterns to parse logs and YAML scenario to identify behaviors. CrowdSec is engineered for modern Cloud / Containers / VM based infrastructures (by decoupling detection and remediation). Once detected, you can remedy threats with various bouncers (firewall block, nginx http 403, Captchas, etc.) while the aggressive IPs can be sent to CrowdSec for curation before being shared among all users to further strengthen the community</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T13:22:18.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"DopplerHQ/awesome-interview-questions","categoryHTML":"<h2>Programming Languages/Frameworks/Platforms</h2><h3>jQuery</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.techgeekbuzz.com/top-jquery-interview-questions/\">Top JQuery Interview Questions and Answers</a></li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T12:59:03.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"golemfactory/awesome-golem","categoryHTML":"<h2>Apps</h2><h3>VPN</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/golemfactory/ya-httpx-client/tree/johny-b/vpn\">Yagna httpx client</a> - VPN usage on Yagna demonstrating communication with a provider-based HTTP server the way you communicate with any other HTTP server.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-08T10:16:16.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"fkromer/awesome-ros2","categoryHTML":"<h2>Operating systems</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Lien182/ReconROS\">ReconROS</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Lien182/ReconROS\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;backg